ActExplosives Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the EXPLOSIVES REGULATIONS USER FEES to make changes to the Explosives User Fees and to update the current fees, which were set in 1993. The proposed revised fees reflect a more appropriate division of costs between the public and private sector and more accurately reflect the 2008 costs of operating the explosives regulatory program.
